   <body>
      <context>
         <p>The radiator cap is located on the left side of the lift truck.</p>
         <note type="warning">
            <p>Hot oil and components can cause personal injury. Do not allow hot oil or components to
        contact skin.</p>
         </note>
         <fig id="fig_uk4_cqz_5gc">
            <image href="media/image867.png" id="image_wk4_cqz_5gc" placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Remove the radiator cap slowly to relieve pressure.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Inspect the cap for damage, deposits or foreign material. Clean the cap with a clean cloth
        or change the cap as necessary.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Install the cap.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
